00:17:04,958 --> 00:17:07,375
Makishima played
them like violins.

286
00:17:07,458 --> 00:17:09,041
Wait. If you're
right about all this,

287
00:17:09,125 --> 00:17:11,458
then the masks are just
the first part of his plan.

288
00:17:11,541 --> 00:17:13,250
We should suppose
that everything

