00:17:13,333 --> 00:17:15,500
is going exactly as he wanted.

290
00:17:15,583 --> 00:17:19,333
And that he predicted the
MWPSB's reaction as well.

291
00:17:21,291 --> 00:17:23,583
Quick Inspector. Can you
bring up all the riot locations.

