00:17:23,666 --> 00:17:27,125
And which areas
we're focusing on first?

293
00:17:27,208 --> 00:17:30,958
Hold on. Here we go.

294
00:17:31,041 --> 00:17:32,541
Looks to me like a feint.

295
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:34,541
What if this thing
was pre-arranged

296
00:17:34,625 --> 00:17:37,000
so that the riots would
intensify at those places just

297
00:17:37,083 --> 00:17:41,166
to lure all the CID detectives
away from their real target?

298
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:50,208
If that's true. Oh no.

299
00:17:53,666 --> 00:17:55,583
These past five years.

300
00:17:55,666 --> 00:17:56,791
I've been trying
to grasp the truth

301
00:17:56,875 --> 00:18:00,125
of the Sibyl System
and how it functions.

302
00:18:00,208 --> 00:18:03,083
Distributed parallel
processing by servers

303
00:18:03,166 --> 00:18:05,416
installed at various
locations around the city.

304
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:08,250
An ideal system of
redundancy and fault tolerance

305
00:18:08,333 --> 00:18:10,500
that could withstand any danger.

306
00:18:10,583 --> 00:18:12,416
Those are the catchphrases
the Ministry of Welfare

307
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:15,375
uses to praise
themselves in the press.

308
00:18:15,458 --> 00:18:17,750
So I started dissecting
their claims.

309
00:18:17,833 --> 00:18:20,500
Measuring and analyzing the
Psycho-Pass of every citizen

