00:19:32,708 --> 00:19:33,916
From a security standpoint,

340
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:36,250
you wouldn't put
everything in one place.

341
00:19:36,333 --> 00:19:38,708
It's too risky,
no matter how you slice it.

342
00:19:38,791 --> 00:19:40,750
Unless they have a secret
so big they'd sooner have the

343
00:19:40,833 --> 00:19:44,541
whole system collapse than let
the public discover the truth.

344
00:19:44,625 --> 00:19:46,416
My thought exactly.

345
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,833
And that's just too
suspicious for me to resist.

346
00:19:48,916 --> 00:19:51,000
When you know there's
something behind the curtain,

347
00:19:51,083 --> 00:19:52,500
you have to look.

348
00:19:53,208 --> 00:19:56,583
It's time to see what the
Sibyl System actually is.

349
00:19:57,166 --> 00:19:59,666
So you tracked it
back to this facility.

