00:20:11,916 --> 00:20:14,208
Plus, there are clear traces

354
00:20:14,291 --> 00:20:17,833
of the power consumption
in this area being faked.

355
00:20:19,541 --> 00:20:21,375
I'm almost positive
that the Sibyl System

356
00:20:21,458 --> 00:20:23,125
is in there somewhere,

357
00:20:23,208 --> 00:20:25,750
inside the Ministry of
Welfare's Nona Tower.

